                             @{b}@{u}Introduction@{ub}@{uu}


Conquest is a one player Mega-lo-Mania clone, a God sim, like Populous 
or Warcraft. Conquest lets you choose to assume leadership for one of these 
civilizations: Roman, British, Hispanic or Gaul.
  


