                          @{b}@{u}Required hardware@{ub}@{uu}


You just need 1Mb chip mem to run the game. Conquest should work under
any Amiga configuration.


Conquest was tested on the following configurations:

    A1200/020/28/4MbFast  - Kickstart 3.1
    A1200/020/14/2MbChip  - Kickstart 3.0

Please let @{" us " Link Author} know if you've got problems running this game.

